fj_mqA ) ; that=E2=80=99s a very useful hedge against hyperscalers abstract=
ing chips away completely so that developers can build models on whatever w=
orks best.

Even there, though, Nvidia is breaking down every barrier to ensure that it=
s chips=E2=80=99 superior performance can be brought to bear. It=E2=80=99s =
a strategy that is working for now, but it=E2=80=99s also an implicit admis=
sion that Nvidia isn=E2=80=99t as integrated in the inference value chain a=
s it might like to be: it wins by being the best, and that=E2=80=99s good e=
nough for now.

